OL,7,FNo: that was the finding from the
OL,8,FSenedd's Children, Young People and
OL,9,FEducation Committee who released their
OL,10,Freport on 16 July after a year-long
OL,11,Fprobe.
OL,13,FIt deemed that access to school was
OL,14,Fnot consistently equal across Wales,
OL,15,Fwith examples of good practice patchy.
OL,16,FThe report said: "Too often, it is too
OL,17,Fdependent on individual staff or
OL,18,Ffamilies working hard. There is no way
OL,19,Fof making sure it happens across
OL,20,FWales."
