OL,7,F"School budgets have been slashed by
OL,8,FLabour, not just in real terms, but in
OL,9,Fcash terms too, which has a knock-on
OL,10,Feffect on adequate ALN provision.
OL,12,F"The Welsh Conservatives would scrap
OL,13,FLabour and Plaid's plans for more
OL,14,Fpoliticians in the Senedd, because
OL,15,Fwe'd rather see taxpayers' money spent
OL,16,Fon more teachers in our classrooms
OL,17,Finstead."
