OL,7,FPlaid Cymru's education spokesperson
OL,8,FCefin Campbell MS said too many
OL,9,Fchildren are being excluded or
OL,10,Fmarginalised through no fault of their
OL,11,Fown, and is calling for more ALN
OL,12,Ftraining plus the recruitment and
OL,13,Ffinancial support for schools to do so.
OL,15,F"With long waits for diagnosis, we
OL,16,Fmust support schools to take a pupil-
OL,17,Fcentred approach from the off," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
